description: Mavshack AB engages in the provision of streaming video-on-demand service. The company is headquartered in Stockholm, Stockholm and currently employs 13 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2008-10-08. The company offers advertising placement, such as pre-roll, mid-roll and post-roll advertisements; small and large productions and live broadcasts in both video and audio; streaming distribution; publishing streamed content online; Facebook development, as well as a range of technology and consulting services. The firm runs and markets the Mavshack.com Website. The firm operates Tradix AB, Cinemaone AB and IP Movers AB as subsidiaries, as well as owns a majority stake in Technologies Manila Inc. The Company’s primary target is the Filipino and Indian diasporas located in North America, the United Kingdom, Middle East and Australia.
